{
  "stem": "19218.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So my friend Joshua and me, and I, we were there for a couple of days.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was too quiet for us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I mean, it was just mountains, a rest place.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We were already used to Brussels, I mean, a city, which was flourishing-- and streetcars, and cars, and theaters.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We-- we-- we decided to forego the vacation, and go back to Brussels.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "My brother stood there all-- all the way through.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "In about November of 1945, somebody came.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And you know, suddenly, you think of your families.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We were trying to find out-- we started writing home to Poland, to see if anybody else survived, if anybody came.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we were corresponding-- the foreman in our brick factory was still there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And the children, they send us back letters that nobody, so far, nobody came.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And then, I had a-- somebody came into a restaurant and told us that they think my sister happens to be in Frankfurt in one of those DP camps, Zalzheim.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They think it is my sister.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And the way they described it, it looked like my sister.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I immediately left for Germany.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, I put on and American uniform, so it would be easier for me to get on a train and cross in there.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "When I arrived in that particular camp, and from the second I arrived, I met that girl.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And unfortunately, I knew that girl.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "She just lived 18 kilometers away from us, in another town.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And she was an-- a spitting image of my sister.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But it wasn't her.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So I immediately left back for Belgium.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We started looking, now, for relatives.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] My brother remembered-- of course, we had an uncle in Costa Rica.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "This I knew.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Because they were first cousins.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
